data.description: This home has lots of character and charm! Located on a large corner lot with plenty of room for parking toys.  Includes a living room and a family room.  Spacious bedrooms and dual sinks in both bathrooms. Additional half bath in laundry room.  Backyard is quiet and inviting with a heated pebble-tech pool and lots of room to entertain.  Pool pump replaced in 2021. Home is on leased solar.
